locations: 613 11th Ave SW Calgary, AB, Canada::(Comedy Monday Night)
imdb.plot outline: Filmed at Canada's premiere open mic comedy room Comedy Monday Night. Stand-up comics from all over test out new jokes then are interviewed in the alley behind the club about their material. The interview takes place outside during the Canadian winter.
imdb.title: After Birth Alley
plot: Stand-up comics birth new jokes on stage then are whisked out to the alley to discuss its conception.::Daryl Makk
